# UI Redesign Plan — GoLive

## Problem
The entire site is broken because [globals.css](file:///C:/GoLive/app/globals.css) is missing:
1. `@import "tailwindcss"` — Tailwind v4 requires this to generate utility classes
2. `@theme { ... }` — custom color tokens must be registered here for classes like `bg-primary` to work

Without these, **every Tailwind class in every component renders as nothing**. The site shows raw unstyled HTML.

## Root Cause Fix

#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///C:/GoLive/app/globals.css)
- Add `@import "tailwindcss"` at the top
- Add `@theme` block with all color/spacing tokens mapped to `--color-*`, `--spacing-*` naming convention
- Add custom component classes for `.glass`, `.btn`, `.no-scrollbar`, etc. inside `@layer components`
- Add `line-clamp`, `aspect-ratio`, and animation utilities

